# ~/.graphify/graphifyignore — OPTIONAL global ignore (general-purpose).
# Read by patch-global-ignore.py as the OUTERMOST (lowest-priority) layer for
# EVERY project, without shadowing per-repo .gitignore/.graphifyignore.
#
# Media (img/video/audio/pdf/office) is NOT handled here anymore — it's a clean
# toggle: `touch ~/.graphify/no-media` (or GRAPHIFY_NO_MEDIA=1) via patch-no-media.py.
# Keeping media out of this file means the toggle can also turn media back ON.
#
# Secrets (.env, *.pem, *.key, id_rsa, credentials, *token*/*secret* ...) are
# skipped by graphify's built-in _is_sensitive in every project regardless.
#
# Add your own global glob excludes below if ever needed (empty by default):
